{
  "stem": "1692.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 408.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They-- they knew that the Germans are gonna be with them-- good to them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Correct.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Correct.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, two days before the Germans attacked, we received a postcard from him saying, I wish I could tell you something, but I can't.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But please send me food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Food.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But we never made it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We started to make bundles.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We never sent it, because it was--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was written in Jewish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The postcard--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--did-- told us that something that he knew and didn't tell us-- for fear, I guess.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The day the Germans attacked, whoever ran away to Russia was there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Other people went into hiding to different places.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And because it was a border town, there was street fights for a whole week.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And every time the Germans would open up a house and come in and see there were Jews, they would say to us, you'll be lucky if the SS won't come by.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because we didn't know anything about that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was street fights for a whole week.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And after that, the Germans took over.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when the Germans took over, we all came out from the hiding places.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's when the bad things started to happen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It didn't take a few weeks, maybe two weeks, that we were told to take only what we can carry.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They're gonna resettle us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they herded us up in the square.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The sick were taken out of the hospitals on stretchers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then we were told to leave everything on the sidewalk and start marching in the middle of the street, 'cause Jewish people were not allowed to walk on the sidewalk.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then we noticed young Ukrainian men marching on the sidewalk with shovels on their shoulders-- singing.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
